IMDb: Who Makes Good/Bad Movies?

Instruction
探討IMDb資料集(https://www.imdb.com/interfaces/) 中，劇組成員以及電影評分之間的關係。
  1. Import, merge, & data description: 讀取與整併資料，觀察電影評分的分布。
  2. Who is most likeky to be in a bad/good movie?: 以第一、第三四分位數區分電影好壞，再看看哪些人最常出現在好/壞電影。
  3. Mean rating of each crew: 計算每個劇組人員其出現的電影之平均分數並排名。
  4. Who’s the highest/lowest rated double?: 將兩個劇組人員合作時的平均分數排名。
  5. Cluster for crews: 嘗試將劇組人員合作的網絡轉為鄰接矩陣，進行hierachical clustering以及 Spectral clustring。
  6. Community analysis: 利用網絡進行community analysis，了解網絡中有哪些小群體，並看那些小群體有最高/最低的平均得分並且視覺化。
  7. Make Predictive Model through Scikit-Learn: 將電影依評分的中數二分，並嘗試以SGDClassifier建立預測性模型。

4. Who’s the highest/lowest rated double?

上面都是以個人為單位分析，接下來要看當兩個人同時出現時其平均得分。

4.1 Finding doubles appears >= 3 times

創建一network_df，將每一部電影中出現的所有兩人排列組合(nconst與next_nconst欄位)。 篩選出出現大於等於三次的雙人組合，並將他們的平均得分與出現次數存在double_rating這個dataframe。

network_df <- df %>%
  filter(titleType == "movie") %>% 
  filter(numVotes >= 10) %>% 
  select(tconst, nconst, averageRating) %>% 
  group_by(tconst) %>% 
  arrange(desc(nconst)) %>% 
  mutate(next_nconst = lag(nconst)) %>% 
  filter(!is.na(next_nconst)) %>% 
  ungroup() %>% 
  select(-tconst) %>%  
  mutate(id1 = as.numeric(substr(nconst, 3, length(nconst))),
         id2 = as.numeric(substr(next_nconst, 3, length(next_nconst)))) %>% 
  mutate(new_nconst = ifelse(id1 > id2, next_nconst, nconst),
         new_next_nconst = ifelse(id1 > id2, nconst, next_nconst)) %>% 
  mutate(nconst = new_nconst, next_nconst = new_next_nconst) %>%
  select(nconst, next_nconst, averageRating) 

network_df_flt <- network_df %>%
  count(nconst, next_nconst) %>% 
  filter(n>=3)

double_rating <- network_df %>%
  right_join(network_df_flt, by = c("nconst", "next_nconst")) %>% 
  group_by(nconst, next_nconst) %>% 
  mutate(double_average_rating = mean(averageRating)) %>% 
  select(-averageRating) %>% 
  slice(1)

head(double_rating)

Merge tables: 將所有人的id與姓名存在crew_name，並用double_rating與crew_name、crew_main_cat left_join，得到nconst與next_nconst的姓名與分類。

5.1.2 Make clusters

分群後可以發現，雖然Silhouette method建議以k=3進行分群，但分群的結果是3個點自己一群，其他點則是另一群，是非常不理想的分群結果。這可能是因為鄰接矩陣過於稀疏的關係，因此下部分改用Spectral clustring進行嘗試。

hc_cluster_tree <- hclust(d, method = "average")
hc_cluster <- cutree(hc_cluster_tree, k=3)
V(g)$hc_cluster <- hc_cluster

df_cluster <- igraph::as_data_frame(g, what = "vertices") %>% 
  left_join(crew_average_rating %>% slice(1) %>% select(nconst, crew_average_rating),
            by = c("name" = "nconst"))
df_cluster %>% 
  group_by(hc_cluster) %>% 
  summarise(n = n(),
            mean_rating = mean(crew_average_rating))

5.2 Spectral clustring

5.2.1 Define matrics & determine k

定義make_affinity函數，可將similarity matrix轉為affinity matrix。

# reference: http://www.di.fc.ul.pt/~jpn/r/spectralclustering/spectralclustering.html
make_affinity <- function(S, n.neighboors=2) {
  N <- length(S[,1])

  if (n.neighboors >= N) {  # fully connected
    A <- S
  } else {
    A <- matrix(rep(0,N^2), ncol=N)
    for(i in 1:N) { # for each line
      # only connect to those points with larger similarity 
      best.similarities <- sort(S[i,], decreasing=TRUE)[1:n.neighboors]
      for (s in best.similarities) {
        j <- which(S[i,] == s)
        A[i,j] <- S[i,j]
        A[j,i] <- S[i,j] # to make an undirected graph, ie, the matrix becomes symmetric
      }
    }
  }
  A  
}
Aff <- make_affinity(S, 3)
D <- diag(apply(Aff, 1, sum))
U <- D - Aff

利用U矩陣的特徵值排序，可以得到最佳的分群數為3。

k <- 2 #降到2維空間
evL <- eigen(U, symmetric = T)
Z <- evL$vectors[ ,(ncol(evL$vectors)-k+1):ncol(evL$vectors)]

plot(1:10, rev(evL$values)[1:10])
abline(v=3.25, col="red", lty=2)

Spectral clustering的分群結果也呈現兩個點自己一群，其他全部點為一群。可能因為這個矩陣過於稀疏，不適用於這些分群的算法。

sp_cluster <- kmeans(Z, centers=3, nstart=5)
V(g)$cluster <- sp_cluster$cluster

df_cluster <- igraph::as_data_frame(g, what = "vertices") %>% 
  left_join(crew_average_rating %>% slice(1) %>% select(nconst, crew_average_rating),
            by = c("name" = "nconst"))
df_cluster %>% 
  group_by(cluster) %>% 
  summarise(n = n(),
            mean_rating = mean(crew_average_rating))

6. Community analysis

上述分群的演算法都無法讓我們了解crews彼此聚集的狀況，但我們可以利用網絡中的communities，也就是網絡中的小群體來了解這些電影工作者彼此的連結。 ##Using leading eigenvalue of modularity matrix to form communities 使用igraph套件中的cluster_leading_eigen函式，利用leading eigenvalue method建立communities。
由結果可見此網絡可分為1103個communities。

community <- cluster_leading_eigen(g, weights=E(g)$n)

6.4 Visualization of communities over 5 members

利用visNetwork套件將網絡中，超過5人的community視覺化。(若沒有出現要等他跑一下) 該網絡圖為可互動式，可以進行縮放、點擊、拖曳等動作。
可以看到該網絡分成一個個小群體，利用左上角的選單選取community，會發現每個小群體與community的分類是一致的。
另外視覺化中，透過顏色來區分category，透過點擊node也可以看到實際連結的情況，放大則可以清楚看到每個點的姓名。

library(visNetwork)
g <- graph_from_data_frame(double_rating %>% select(nconst, next_nconst, n, double_average_rating), directed = F, vertices = nodes_df)

sub_g <- induced_subgraph(g, which(V(g)$community %in% community_over_5$community))

sub_g_vis <- toVisNetworkData(sub_g)
sub_g_vis$nodes <- sub_g_vis$nodes %>%
  rename(group = main_category, id = label, label = primaryName) 

visNetwork(nodes = sub_g_vis$nodes, edges = sub_g_vis$edges) %>% 
    visInteraction(navigationButtons = TRUE) %>% 
    visOptions(highlightNearest = TRUE, selectedBy  = "community") %>% 
    visLegend(width = 0.2, position = "right", main = "Category")

7. Make Predictive Model through Scikit-Learn

本部分將電影依rating中數區二分為好/壞，並以每個劇組成員是否出現的sparse matrix進行預策性建模。
由於sklearn.feature_extraction.text中的CountVectorizer可以幫我們建立sparse matrix，因此先在r中建立movie_good_or_bad的dataframe，共三個欄位:電影id、劇組成員(以空白分隔)，是否是好電影(1/0)。之後再用python讀取該檔案進行建模。

總共有42855部電影，234337個劇組人員。

const <- df %>% 
  select(tconst, nconst) %>% 
  filter(tconst %in% movie_df$tconst) %>% 
  left_join(movie_df %>% select(tconst, averageRating),
            by = "tconst") %>% 
  mutate(good_or_bad = ifelse(averageRating > median(movie_df$averageRating), 1, 0))
const %>% count(nconst) %>% nrow()
## [1] 234337

一部電影最多有10個crew

df$ordering %>% max()
## [1] 10

建立movie_good_or_bad dataframe

movie_good_or_bad <- const %>% 
  arrange(tconst) %>% 
  group_by(tconst) %>% 
  mutate(nconst_1 = lag(nconst, 1)) %>% 
  mutate(nconst_2 = lag(nconst, 2)) %>% 
  mutate(nconst_3= lag(nconst, 3)) %>%
  mutate(nconst_4= lag(nconst, 4)) %>%
  mutate(nconst_5= lag(nconst, 5)) %>%
  mutate(nconst_6= lag(nconst, 6)) %>%
  mutate(nconst_7= lag(nconst, 7)) %>%
  mutate(nconst_8= lag(nconst, 8)) %>%
  mutate(nconst_9= lag(nconst, 9)) %>% 
  mutate(nconst_1 = ifelse(is.na(nconst_1), "", nconst_1),
         nconst_2 = ifelse(is.na(nconst_2), "", nconst_2),
         nconst_3 = ifelse(is.na(nconst_3), "", nconst_3),
         nconst_4 = ifelse(is.na(nconst_4), "", nconst_4),
         nconst_5 = ifelse(is.na(nconst_5), "", nconst_5),
         nconst_6 = ifelse(is.na(nconst_6), "", nconst_6),
         nconst_7 = ifelse(is.na(nconst_7), "", nconst_7),
         nconst_8 = ifelse(is.na(nconst_8), "", nconst_8),
         nconst_9 = ifelse(is.na(nconst_9), "", nconst_9)) %>% 
  unite(col = "crews",  c(nconst, nconst_1:nconst_9), sep = " ") %>% 
  slice(n())
movie_good_or_bad <- movie_good_or_bad %>% select(-averageRating)

7.2 Make prdictive model

Import needed modules

from sklearn.feature_extraction.text import CountVectorizer
from sklearn.linear_model import SGDClassifier
from sklearn.model_selection import  StratifiedKFold, GridSearchCV
from sklearn.pipeline import Pipeline
from sklearn.feature_selection import SelectPercentile, chi2
from sklearn.metrics import f1_score, accuracy_score
import numpy as np

使用SGDClassifier為模型，chi square值為feature selection基準，並調整選取變項數（在本模型中等於所有劇組人數）的百分比。
模型會經過k=4的cross-validation，以這4次平均的accuracy score、f1 score為判斷模型好壞的基準。

skf =  StratifiedKFold(n_splits = 4, shuffle = True, random_state=47)
all_accuracy_list = []
all_f1_list = []
for train_index, test_index in skf.split(movie.crews, movie.good_or_bad):
    X_train, X_test = movie.crews[train_index], movie.crews[test_index]
    y_train, y_test = movie.good_or_bad[train_index], movie.good_or_bad[test_index]

    accuracy_list = []
    f1_list = []

    for p in range(10, 101, 10):
        pipeline = Pipeline([
            ('vect', CountVectorizer()),
            ('chi_2', SelectPercentile(chi2, percentile=p)),
            ('clf', SGDClassifier())
            ])
        pipeline.fit(X_train, y_train)
        y_pred = pipeline.predict(X_test)

        accuracy = accuracy_score(y_test, y_pred)
        f1 = f1_score(y_test, y_pred)

        accuracy_list.append(accuracy)
        f1_list.append(f1)
    all_accuracy_list.append(accuracy_list)
    all_f1_list.append(f1_list)
acc_array = np.array(all_accuracy_list)
mean_acc = np.mean(acc_array, axis = 0)

f1_array = np.array(all_f1_list)
mean_f1 = np.mean(f1_array, axis = 0)

7.3 Visualization of model tuning

由下圖可知，在用chi square選擇小於20%或高於90%左右的變項時本模型會有較好的表現。

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

plt_df = pd.DataFrame({'x': list(range(10, 101, 10)), 'Accuracy': mean_acc, 'F1' : mean_f1})

plt.plot('x', 'Accuracy', data = plt_df)
plt.plot('x', 'F1', data = plt_df)
plt.xlabel('Select Percentile(%)')
plt.ylabel('score')
plt.legend()
plt.show()

7.4 Hyperparameter Tuning

使用GridSearchCV，校調chi square篩選變項的百分比、SGDClassifier中的loss function以及regularization term。
結果顯示，chi square feature selecotr保留10%變項, 以hinge為SGDClassifier的loss function（等同SVC），正規化參數0.0001可以得到最佳的模型。

param_grid = [{'chi_2__percentile': [10, 20, 80, 90, 100],
               'clf__loss':['log', 'hinge'],
               'clf__alpha': np.logspace(-4, 0, 3)}]

pipeline = Pipeline([
        ('vect', CountVectorizer()),
        ('chi_2', SelectPercentile(chi2)),
        ('clf', SGDClassifier())
        ])

gscv = GridSearchCV(pipeline, cv=5, param_grid=param_grid, scoring="f1")
gscv.fit(movie.crews, movie.good_or_bad)
print(gscv.best_params_)
## {'chi_2__percentile': 10, 'clf__alpha': 0.0001, 'clf__loss': 'hinge'}
print(gscv.best_score_)
## 0.6780424160840899

7.5 Crew with best chi square

上述使用chi square為feature selction的方法，也可以幫助我們了解那些變項（在本模型中即是哪些crew）在好/壞電影上較有區辨力。選取chi square最高的10個crew，再回去看他們的平均得分。

vectorizer = CountVectorizer()
vect = vectorizer.fit_transform(movie.crews)

chi_score = chi2(vect, movie.good_or_bad)
best_chi_id = chi_score[0].argsort()[-10:]

best_chi_crew = [vectorizer.get_feature_names()[i] for i in best_chi_id]
best_chi_crew
## ['nm0725808', 'nm1700105', 'nm0001803', 'nm0159008', 'nm0827500', 'nm0000514', 'nm0940598', 'nm1413593', 'nm0000616', 'nm0490375']
